en_231426_0	A businessman has been shot and killed in Ragama - Ganemulla.
en_231426_1	The police media unit noted that the shooting occurred around 7.50 last night.
en_231426_2	Owing to the shooting a 30 year old businessman from Mattegoda who had been renting out vehicles was killed.
en_231426_3	He had been in Ragama last night to hand over a van on rent.
en_231426_4	A family from Italy who is in country for vacation had rented the van for temporary use.
en_231426_5	Police noted that upon handing over the vehicle to the family, the businessman was shot by an individual in a car.
en_231426_6	The suspect who had shot at the businessman was arrested early this morning.
en_231426_7	The suspect is a resident of Ragama and was arrested while he was in hiding at his fathers residence in Welisara- Thaappawaththa.
en_231426_8	A 9mm revolver used for the shooting was also seized by the police.
en_231426_9	Further investigations revealed that the suspect had been an army deserter.
en_231426_10	It has also been revealed that the deceased entrepreneur was a friend of the suspect and the reason behind the shooting has not been revealed.
